Create a class Product

    - productId which could be string or int(decide by user who gives data)
    - productName hwich is a string
    - productPrice which is a float value

    Create getter, setters and all relevant special member functions as applicable

Create the following functionalities 

    - A function that returns average Product price from a container of products
    - A function that returns a container pof all product instances whose price 
        is above a threshold value provided as an additional argument
    - A function which launches the following threads
        - a thread to find and display the details of the product whose ID
             is passed as a parmaneter from acontainer of instances.
        - a thread to find and print the details of the first N instances of Product 
            from a container of instances where N is given as an additional parameter. 